highlights.text: “零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 151 days straight.
“Montagem Supersonic” by KHAOS and Jmilton is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 37 spots at #62.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #8.
“Money Loves Me” by Alchemist Harmony is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #16.
